text: Anotosaura collaris, the collared anotosaura, is a species of lizard in the family Gymnophthalmidae. It is endemic to Brazil. ==References== Category:Anotosaura Category:Reptiles of Brazil Category:Endemic fauna of Brazil Category:Reptiles described in 1933 Category:Taxa named by Afrânio Pompílio Gastos do Amaral
